    "category": "regulatory_disclosure",
    "headline": "Bunge Global SA changes segment and volume reporting to align with value chain operating structure following Viterra merger.",
    "narrative_summary": "Bunge Global SA announced changes in its segment and volume reporting to better reflect the combined company's operations post-merger with Viterra. The new segments include Soybean Processing and Refining, Softseed Processing and Refining, Other Oilseeds Processing and Refining, and Grain Merchandising and Milling."
